name: Catversusdog
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cat versus dog
des:
This skill allows you to listen to a series of cat meows and dog barks.
4 modes are available:
- normal mode
- small mode with the meowing of kittens and the barking of puppies
- angry mode with cat screeching and dogs grunting
- XXL mode with meows and barks which are quickly replaced by XXL roars and groans from felines, canines and ursids.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
